sentences.sentence: The trace that we have just dumped from memory to a file named DMP can be parsed or formated into readable text using one or both of the parsing options on the db2trc command.
sentences.translation: 对于我们从内存转储到名为dmp的文件中的跟踪，通过使用db 2 trc命令上的一个或两个解析选项，我们可以对其进行解析，或将其格式化为可读的文本。
